# Tests

## Requirements

- Run `pytest` before every PR; all tests must pass
- New validation/mapping → unit test (no network)
- New MCP tool → async in-process test with `fastmcp.Client` + `create_server()`

## Safe integration queries

```python
{"query": "NC_045512.2", "is_accession": True}
{"preset": "sars_cov2_ref_genome"}
{"accession": "P01308"}  # UniProt
```

Never integration-test unfiltered SARS-CoV-2 (`2697049`) or full dataset downloads without explicit maintainer approval.

## Patterns

- Use `tmp_path` + `monkeypatch.setenv("KIKI_AUDIT_DIR", ...)` for audit tests
- Reproducibility: same params × 3 → identical `query_id` and count
- `@pytest.mark.asyncio` for MCP client tests
